  "text": "Note that S 1 , the coefficient of y in S(y) = yG(1, 1 + y), is exactly G (1, 1) , the length generating function of 1234-avoiding permutations. The expression of S(x) = xG(1, 1+x) is then obtained from [CITATION_1] , and this concludes the proof of Theorem 12.",
